 A WOMAN has beaten her seven-year-old son to death in Agbarha community, Warri South council area of Delta State. The Nation gathered that the incident occurred on Monday evening. A source said, “The mother punished the boy by asking him to ‘ride a bike’ (sit in the air) but the boy was too hungry to do it. She became very angry and flogged  him until he collapsed and died.” Police confirmed the incident, adding that the woman had been arrested. 